From 61d08e6156d611cb4cc80cd1906d6f61a51f0f49 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 12:48:21 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/8] Redesign owner list + invoice screens with v1 system

- Invoice detail uses .doc layout: kicker + invoice number, total-due
  side card, line table, totals stack, activity-style right column.
- Invoices list switches to the v1 stat-grid + tabbed table with pills,
  archived past view grouped biweekly.
- Jobs list adopts .tbl + status/priority pills, orange-soft row for
  completed-uninvoiced jobs, sort headers with arrows.
- Work orders list uses .pill statuses, section headers with mono counts,
  card rows with kicker/tag combos.
